p: A deep study of the anticancer activity of aromadendrene, α-terpinolene, β-selinene, bicyclo-sesquiphellandrene, α-amorphene, 2,3-dihydro-1,8-cineole, calamenene, 2,3-di- tert-butylphenol, bicyclogermacrene and ( E)-β-ocimene will have to be carried out to determine the origin of the anticancer activity of H. gymnocephalum. On the same target, we should evaluate the synergy between these compounds and their own contribution to the final anticancer activity.
